  "summary": "MoinMoin Multiple cross-site scripting (XSS) vulnerabilities",
  "details": "Multiple cross-site scripting (XSS) vulnerabilities in MoinMoin before 1.5.7 allow remote attackers to inject arbitrary web script or HTML via (1) the page info, or the page name in a (2) AttachFile, (3) RenamePage, or (4) LocalSiteMap action.",
